narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Learned to think critically and creatively about science, got to put class knowledge to practical use. Also learned about lab dynamic and how to communicate in difficult situations.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Poor mentorship and communication this semester made research difficult. More concrete mentorship expectations would be valuable.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Would recommend research for credit if you definitely have a good mentor and project already set up.
